{"tid":1508502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解大家會嬲？","createTime":"2019-08-26T14:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T14:19:22.000Z","uid":2719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eeaa1384191c52f01ee90083906c7a326c9a4236","tid":1508502,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:14:53.000Z","msg":"- 撒回有難度<br />\n- 在任期絕不會成立獨會<br />\n<br />\n明明係一件好事，繼續火上加油。<br />\n如果放軟，就會有人收貨，場運動就完。<br />\n（原諒我仲未叫得岀係革命）<br />\n<br />\n唔係為玩而玩，依家唔一鋪清袋，<br />\n拎一兩個甜頭就完即係等清算。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可唔係口號咁簡單，<br />\n係真係要做到先收貨，否則唔好講預咗攬炒。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家態度正面啲，唔好俾怒火影響判斷。<br />\n依家柒婆助攻我地，我地要繼續努力打好呢場仗！"},{"pid":"80545b80c1cd0052a57cb2b1613006304c54db5a","tid":1508502,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=7c27c16e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=152794c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=e2277907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"}]}